answers.answer: Congrats! I'm due May 31st too but I feel like I'm gonna have to be induced ): I haven't been having any contractions what so ever!
I was having contractions for weeks aND actually had my induction scheduled for the 24th due to gestational diabetes

question: I wasn't due until may 31st. My water broke at 230 am Monday the 11th.  After 36 hours of labor and pushing for 3 hours I ended up having a csection because baby was not coming down any.  I wanted to avoid a csection at all costs.  But when he came out he was having difficulty breathing so he went to the NICU for 40 hours.  The hospital I'm at has been amazing with my wishes to breastfeed. and we should be going home.  But baby was born at 37 weeks 2 days at 9 lb 7 oz and 21 inches long.
title: Baby came early
